To start the capture, run the following command:

adb shell am startservice -n com.nvidia.NvCapTest/.NvCapTest --es com.nvidia.NvCapTest.NvCapControl start

To update parameters at runtime (FPS, BPS, force an IDR picture), run the following command:

adb shell am startservice -n com.nvidia.NvCapTest/.NvCapTest --es com.nvidia.NvCapTest.NvCapControl runtime

To end the capture, run the following command:

adb shell am startservice -n com.nvidia.NvCapTest/.NvCapTest --es com.nvidia.NvCapTest.NvCapControl end
